      "raw_text": "of the c. 4 G. mill at the foot of\nPost street must be torn down with\nin the next 10 days.\n\n\nThe board of public works has sent\nword several times to the water\npower company to tear down the\nruins and remove the unsightly and\ncharred frame as well as avert any\ndanger of collapse of the remains of\nthe big mill, but no attention has\nbeen paid.\n\n\nThe notice today is expected to be\nrecognized by the water power COM\npany, but in the event the company\ndoes not obey legal steps will be\ntaken."
